title: 2116 - Dynasty Sweats
description:
MATERIAL: 100% Cotton. French Terry.

FABRIC WEIGHT: 460 GSM.

FIT: Baggy.

DESIGN: Inspired by the classic Immortal Joggers, the Dynasty Sweats bring a fresh twist with a modern, no-cuff baggy fit. Made from 100% premium cotton with an acid-washed finish, these joggers feature a bold distressed and splatter print down one leg for a unique look.

MODEL: The model in the first photo is wearing a size Medium. Weight: 175lb Height: 5'9.
